Program: Great Lives
Title: Ray Mears on Rommel
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b04f9r9m
Last Broadcast Date: Tue 26 Aug 2014
The life of Erwin Rommel, for a time Hitler's favourite general is nominated by Ray Mears. Matthew Parris hears why this German soldier was a "great life". They are also joined by Dr Niall Barr, Reader in Military History, Defence Studies Department at Kings College, London. Producer: Perminder Khatkar. Show less